{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/GIF__1_.gif?t=1737689054\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/ph2.png?t=1737689054\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you ever wanted to feel like a military commander, now is your chance.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Roguelike elements: achievements with rewards on new games.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Management of resources</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Event system with 4 polls for each day (night camp, morning event, strategic choices and tactical deployment)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Squad-based real-time tactics combat (with an optional active pause mode) / Real Time Strategy </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unit customization (Level up skills mechanics,\u00a0Equipment upgrades)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/Untitled-12.png?t=1737689054\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/ph1.png?t=1737689054\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A mysterious deadly plague has infected the city of Sun Stone, and all communications with the city administration have been cut off.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are the appointed commander who must assemble a strike team and deploy them within the epicenter to find answers before the plague spreads beyond the city limits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/more_infected.png?t=1737689054\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will get to make strategic decisions that will impact the status, supplies, and sanity of your squad, and tactical decisions that will impact the survival chances of your strike team during combat engagement with the creatures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The lives of your men are in your hands and the story will be shaped according to your choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/ph3.png?t=1737689054\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game is rather short but emphasizes the replayability factor making each playthrough as unique and fresh as possible by giving you different new games</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">bonus options, a bit of randomly generated content, achievements with rewards on the next game, multiple strategic choices with various outcomes, multiple paths, multiple endings and multiple ways to play.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/ezgif-2-3702136f1d.gif?t=1737689054\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fair Warning: the game can become very hard if you get too greedy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/ph4.png?t=1737689054\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game has a Lovecraftian - Military theme, mixing Real-time strategy gameplay with heavy Horror elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015620/extras/Untitled-4vdvdvdv.png?t=1737689054\" /></p><p 